just be more personal. Don't be
a machine. Don't let the

34:04.910 --> 34:06.478 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
consultants control everything.

34:06.478 --> 34:10.148 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Very quickly, you
mentioned Jeb Bush this week.

34:10.148 --> 34:13.385 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
