34:45.850 --> 34:46.818 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What do you make of this?

34:46.818 --> 34:49.421 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARK SHIELDS: It's a
problem for Jeb Bush.

34:49.421 --> 34:52.958 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Jeb Bush is trying to get back
on stride. He's trying to get
