Dick Cheney and Don Rumsfeld?

35:11.109 --> 35:16.715 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
It has always mystified
everybody who knew the first
President Bush why W. ever chose

35:16.715 --> 35:20.518 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Don Rumsfeld, who had actually
knifed Bush 41, his father...

35:20.518 --> 35:23.288 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: His father, yes.

35:23.288 --> 35:29.294 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: ... and really was
-- and then, of course,
administered the coup in his
rebuttal

35:29.294 --> 35:34.566 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about the book by saying, well,
he's obviously getting up in
years and he's too old,
something

35:34.566 --> 35:38.803 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that Jon Meacham put to -- I
thought to rest in his interview
with you, that he was very

35:38.803 --> 35:40.939 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
much alert and
involved and engaged.

35:40.939 --> 35:42.173 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: That's
exactly what he said.

35:42.173 --> 35:45.443 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Is this the kind of thing
the matters today, David?

35:45.443 --> 35:48.513 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Well, it will hurt
-- it will be a distraction for
Bush. But Bush is at

35:48.513 --> 35:52.884 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
4 percent. He has got
bigger -- bigger problems.

35:52.884 --> 35:58.256 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the things the elder Bush
said, the younger Bush, W. Bush,
believed by 2005. This was

35:58.256 --> 36:00.158 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
