these interviews were done in
'08 and '10.

36:00.158 --> 36:00.025 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: That's right.

36:00.025 --> 36:01.559 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
