36:01.559 --> 36:04.195 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: And so George W.
Bush had come to these views
about Cheney and Rumsfeld at

36:04.195 --> 36:06.564 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
