big differences between the two.

36:23.048 --> 36:26.885 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, there is a lot of
interesting stuff in there. I'm
struck by Bush family reticence.

36:26.885 --> 36:29.354 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And we see it hurting
Jeb these days.

36:29.354 --> 36:35.126 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: I always thought
that the piece signed in The
Wall Street Journal by Jim Baker

36:35.126 --> 36:35.560 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
and...

36:35.560 --> 36:36.928 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID BROOKS: Scowcroft.

36:36.928 --> 36:38.196 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARK SHIELDS: ... and
Brent Scowcroft...

36:38.196 --> 36:39.831 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Brent Scowcroft.

36:39.831 --> 36:45.503 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: ... his national
security adviser and his closest
political adviser, warning

36:45.503 --> 36:50.942 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
against the invasion by the
United States of Iraq, was the
memo to Bush 41 to Bush 43,

36:50.942 --> 36:53.378 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
which he chose to ignore.

36:53.378 --> 36:55.814 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And when Bob Woodward asked him
if he talked to his father, he
said, "I speak to my divine

36:55.814 --> 36:57.248 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
father."

36:57.248 --> 36:57.715 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: That's right, the
higher father. He said higher
father.

36:57.715 --> 36:58.383 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

36:58.383 --> 36:58.850 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARK SHIELDS: The higher
father. Higher father.

36:58.850 --> 37:00.185 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Yes.

37:00.185 --> 37:01.719 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: I mean, thus
putting him in his place.

37:01.719 --> 37:04.289 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All right.

37:04.289 --> 37:06.958 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
