44:18.923 --> 44:22.727 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
of marketing and commercialism.

44:22.727 --> 44:28.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
"Honky" is a satirical comedy
about five people attempting to
navigate the dicey waters of

44:28.966 --> 44:32.336 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
race, rhetoric and basketball
shoes. A performance of the play
was taped at the San Diego
Repertory

44:32.336 --> 44:33.304 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Theatre.

44:33.304 --> 44:35.806 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And the author, Greg
Kalleres, joins me know.

44:35.806 --> 44:37.041 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, thank you for joining me.

44:37.041 --> 44:39.710 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
First of all, why this play?

44:39.710 --> 44:41.812 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GREG KALLERES, Playwright,
"Honky": Well, I worked in
advertising. I kind of stumbled

44:41.812 --> 44:43.681 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
