forced to speak comfortably
about something that they were

44:59.363 --> 45:00.631 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
clearly not comfortable.

45:00.631 --> 45:01.832 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ACTOR: Would you wear these?

