45:21.052 --> 45:25.456 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
say when that guy is in
the room is fascinating.

45:25.456 --> 45:29.560 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTOR: For the last 15 years,
