the closest you get to making

48:33.010 --> 48:36.881 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
them scared, or
offended, or upset.

48:36.881 --> 48:38.983 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
ACTOR: I run an
urban shoe company.

48:38.983 --> 48:41.652 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ACTOR: Urban?

48:41.652 --> 48:47.258 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ACTOR: It's a euphemism for
