Tallison. You can simply use...

48:56.567 --> 48:57.568 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ACTOR: Urban.

48:57.568 --> 48:59.103 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ACTOR: I was going
to say a pronoun.

48:59.103 --> 49:01.005 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ACTOR: Oh.

49:01.005 --> 49:04.175 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ACTOR: I sell basketball
shoes to them.

49:04.175 --> 49:06.510 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ACTOR: Well, now the
pronoun is offensive.

49:06.510 --> 49:07.745 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

49:07.745 --> 49:12.783 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ACTOR: My overall point is,
I don't think I'm a racist.

49:12.783 --> 49:14.952 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
