49:38.442 --> 49:40.811 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ACTOR: I'm getting married soon.

49:40.811 --> 49:41.779 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ACTRESS: Congratulations.

