50:57.288 --> 50:58.656 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Homogenize it.

50:58.656 --> 51:01.025 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
GREG KALLERES: Exactly,
